_json.gridTitle: Can I Wash My Hair After Dyeing It? Hairstylists Weigh In
_json.description: PS: Has this always been your technique? When did you see it start to catch fire? ACT: Over the years, it's one thing I for sure always loved, but I never "got" it. I never got to the point where I could reduplicate it. And that's the thing when you're a young stylist. I would do trial and error, and I'd fine-tune it, and I'd think "let's find a process to formulate, a process to achieve this look." It took me 10-12 years to say, "Sh*t, I can do this on every type of hair!" But it's not ...
